//Pseudocode to check weather the given number is even or odd 
//after calculation of it's square or cube
Start

    Prompt the user to enter a number
    Read the input number and store it in a variable num

    If num mod 2 is equal to 0
        Set result = num * num     //(square of num)
        Print "The square of ", num, " is ", result
    
    Else
        Set result = num * num * num      //(cube of num)
        Print "The cube of ", num, " is ", result
    EndIf

End